OL,5, Boris Becker, the six-time Grand Slam  
OL,6, tennis champion, offered his wedding   
OL,7, ring in a bid to pay off his debts, a  
OL,8, court has heard.                       
OL,10,FMr Becker also wanted to sell his      
OL,11,FMallorca estate in an effort to cancel 
OL,12,Fhis bankruptcy, the jury was told.     
OL,14,FThe 54-year-old German national was    
OL,15,Fdeclared bankrupt in June 2017 after   
OL,16,Fborrowing more than #3m from a bank.   
OL,18,FHe is on trial at Southwark Crown Court
OL,19,Fcharged with 24 offences under the     
OL,20,FInsolvency Act. He denies all charges. 
